data.description: Short Sale. SHORT SALE! All offers will be entertained! Potential to get a good deal if the bank accepts your offer! Welcome to your dream home at 2572 Partridge Dr in the charming city of Winter Haven, Florida! This stunning property is a true gem, offering a perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern elegance. Located in a gated community within a tranquil and peaceful neighborhood, this home is a haven for those seeking a retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and open floor plan that fills every corner of the home with an abundance of natural light. The rich hardwood flooring and tray ceilings add a touch of sophistication to the interior, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertaining. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the beautifully renovated kitchen, complete with granite countertops and a large pantry. It's a chef's delight, where you can whip up gourmet meals or enjoy casual family gatherings with ease. With generously-sized bedrooms and ample closet space, this home ensures everyone has their own comfortable sanctuary. The spaciousness extends to the oversized 3-car garage, providing ample storage for your vehicles and belongings. But the real showstopper is the large outdoor patio with a large pool and a screened-in pool cage. Whether you're lounging in the sun or hosting a poolside barbecue, this outdoor oasis is perfect for making lasting memories with friends and family. This property offers not only a beautifully appointed home but also a lifestyle tailored to relaxation and tranquility. The gated community provides an extra layer of security and privacy, and the quiet neighborhood creates a serene backdrop for your daily life. The motivated seller is eager to pass on this incredible opportunity to a new owner who will cherish and enjoy this remarkable property as much as they have. Don't miss your chance to own this piece of paradise in Winter Haven, Florida. Schedule your viewing today and make 2572 Partridge Dr your forever home! Property sold as-is, seller will make no repairs.
